---
title: One-Pan Cantina Shrimp Fajitas with Spicy Guacamole & Smoky Red Pepper Crema
description: Tonight’s meal is quick, easy, and downright delicious. It’s got it all—we’re talking spiced shrimp, sautéed poblano, and onion, all tossed with lime juice for a tangy punch. The joyous jumble gets piled into steamy flour tortillas along with spicy guacamole, a drizzle of smoky red pepper crema, and a dash of hot sauce if you like a little extra kick. Talk about a fajita-tastic meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61952aac1e429c3c246b4c40-b1558197.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pan-cantina-shrimp-fajitas-61952aac1e429c3c246b4c40-b28e5df6.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pan-cantina-shrimp-fajitas-61952aac1e429c3c246b4c40
servings: 2
author: Sara Heilman
time required: 20 minutes
course: main course
cuisine: Mexican
nutrition:
  calories: 660 kcal
  fat: 27 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
  carbohydrates: 73 g
